<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hurry-v">hurry <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hʌri/    美 /'hɜːri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-rush">1.★ <strong>（朝某方向）迅速移动（rush）:</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I hurried to the store,I saw that the books were already being packed into boxes.
当我匆忙赶到店里时，看到那些书已经被装进箱子里了。</p><footer>外研新选必② – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-rush">2.★ <strong>(使) 赶紧；匆忙 (做) (rush)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A good meal should never be hurried.
美食不应狼吞虎咽。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There's no need to hurry. We've got plenty of time.
不必着急，我们有的是时间。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>催促：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hurry him, or he'll be late.
催他一下，不然他要迟到了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="hurry-on">hurry on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>喋喋不休；啰嗦得没完没了</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="hurry-up">hurry up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[口语] 快点；(使) 加快：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You'll be late if you don't hurry up.
如果你不快点就要迟到了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hurry her up! We are all waiting for her.
叫她快点！我们都在等着她呢。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please hurry up the dinner.
请催一下快点开饭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Just a moment. I haven't finished packing my suitcase.
— Hurry <strong><em>_</em></strong>__. It's high time we left for the airport.  （2011 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. up  </p></div>